Class AttributeType.DefaultImpls

  • com.hp.jipp.encoding.AttributeType.DefaultImpls
  • Enclosing interface:
    AttributeType<T>

    public static class AttributeType.DefaultImpls

    A named attribute type which may be used to construct interface Attribute objects containing values of type T.

    See Also:
    interface Attribute
